snippet.title: JungleTac 16-in-1 - Tiger Rescue (GBA)
snippet.description: Here's the third game from the JungleTac 16-in-1 multicart. This one is basically a rip-off of Aero Fighters. It's not that bad, but the only thing that sucks about it in my opinion is that you start at the beginning at the level again after you've lost all your lives. I still prefer Aero Fighters over this one
